Comment: 1,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.16,Takagisan - text_cn,,0,0,0,,——CN——
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,手都要冻僵了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我特别怕冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要用暖宝宝吗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.09,0:01:52.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.97,0:02:02.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,冰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好厚的冰啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天下雨了嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是想把它带回家了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.86,0:02:19.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小学生
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来比赛吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 要比什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,比谁拿到校门口的冰块更大
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 中途要是冰掉在地上的话就算输
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.02,0:02:51.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你先请
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那我开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿了大块的冰诶
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能成功带到学校就好了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学 你着急了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我可是绝不会手滑摔碎冰块的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我从小看到冰就一定会带走
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,手指一点也不怕冻
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我绝不会因为冻手就放下冰块的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 对于每天严格坚持
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,做被高木同学捉弄回数3倍量的俯卧撑的我来说
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这点冰根本算不了什么嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就要让你后悔发起这个心血来潮的比赛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天就要输给我了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.33,0:03:48.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉西片拿着大冰块的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,像个开心的小学生似的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…我才没有开心呢…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜呀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有「让对方的冰块滑掉」这种作战吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会再掉以轻心了 今天一定要赢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.45,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你那么用力捏的话 冰块会裂开哦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.33,0:04:32.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,担心敌人吗 你可真从容不迫啊高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.17,0:04:38.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不过的确 不能捏太紧反而捏碎了冰块
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 作为惩罚
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.30,0:04:47.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,输了的人要给赢了的人暖手哦 明白了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我明白了 只要用这个力度的话…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 你刚刚说什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才说
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.85,0:05:00.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,输了的人要给赢了的人暖手
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶——
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.41,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑得太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太弱了吧 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要玩惩罚游戏了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要干什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了嘛 输了的人要给赢了的人暖手啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那是认真的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.77,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以换成别的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说不清
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那不行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给我暖宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真暖和啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,外观
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 高木同学 早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你脸上一副写着「我想到有趣的比赛了」的表情嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.25,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,现在则是「你猜对了」的表情
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以是什么比赛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 反正今天我一定能赢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天的我和昨天有哪里不一样呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来猜吧 是哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是心情上的变化吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是外观哦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道了吧 高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,其实昨晚我剪了一点点头发
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点犯规 倒不如说是有点卑鄙
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但赢了就是赢了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.95,0:07:16.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我再观察一会儿吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想等着我自己说漏嘴吧 可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有哪里不一样了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是背面吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会被她这样盯着看
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.20,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想会不会是在衣服里面
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 是能看见的地方啦
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你太一惊一乍了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.37,0:08:06.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也没想到中途会被这样捉弄
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.68,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,腰这里还是老样子怕痒呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想这么干吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太…太近了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是眼睛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你脸很红哦
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.28,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不一样的难道是脸红吗
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,身上的味道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.21,0:08:44.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没怎么变啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说了嘛 是外观 外观
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.67,0:08:55.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道高木同学其实已经知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了好玩捉弄我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我已经被看穿了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我都完全没想到啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是眼睛吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果害羞的话 也可以认输哦
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.08,0:09:24.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,故意说要我放弃的话
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就说明她并不知道答案
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说只要坚持过这一关 就是我的胜利了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是耳朵吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不对啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来这招啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.49,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,头发
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能短时间改变的只有指甲和头发啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是指甲的话
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.30,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该就是头发吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那作为惩罚
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我也做点外观上的改变哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来轮到西片来猜哦
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道我会害羞 不好意思盯着她看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧 去学校吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也没想到会被她反过来捉弄
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,天气变冷了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.25,0:10:51.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,刘海
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你刘海怎么回事啊 有点奇怪诶
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不许笑
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天自己剪了一下 结果剪多了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 不许笑啦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 太好笑了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你刘海不也像剪毁了一样
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 差不多
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,失败品一样的刘海…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.18,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我还挺喜欢的…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 美奈 我有点说过头了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个刘海很适合你哦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.82,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友的话明明应该要鼓励你的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.33,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我却嘲笑了你
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊 由加莉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.97,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14日
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.35,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 今天也很冷呢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好 高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来啊我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心 要保持平常心啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有体育课吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得好像没有
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢 谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 这里面
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,会有某人塞进来的巧克力什么的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.86,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才打开鞋柜时你好像有点失望
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.03,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.66,0:13:33.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不… 没…没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事…都没有啦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紫式部的源氏物语
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.88,0:13:46.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,清少纳言的枕草子也是研究对象之一
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,老师在读中学的时候也…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.14,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算是情人节
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.02,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没抱有什么期待哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.94,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 倒不如说正是这种日子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.81,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,她才更可能会来捉弄我
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.07,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,提高警戒吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.24,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.16,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能借我一下橡皮擦吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.37,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在还我橡皮擦的时候 若无其事地递给我巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的话要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.42,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.13,0:14:22.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,他这么说耶 太好笑了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.27,0:14:35.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.06,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么送给他呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.07,0:14:43.73,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,大家！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是情人节 我做了很多巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的人请自便
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.91,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧 饱含爱意的手制巧克力？女子力好高
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.96,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要 我也要
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样四处散播自己的爱
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.13,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给我好好地派给大家啊 日比野
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能去拿啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是也有美奈那样的性格就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.40,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发现巧克力就要没收
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.65,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧 日比野
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.20,0:15:34.87,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没收
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.04,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 还得小心老师才行
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我能送出去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.63,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,没收什么的 好过分啊
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我还没拿到…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真是闻者落泪呢 四处散播爱的后果
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.77,0:16:02.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想问你是不是已经送出去了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要问有没有送出去的话 也算是送出去了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早上…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.74,0:16:13.70,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.95,0:16:14.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,高木也觉得害羞吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我无论如何也想亲手送给他
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.46,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉这样才能表达我的心意
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.63,0:16:34.26,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这简直就像是试炼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就在海边啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.64,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.51,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,来看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对很厉害的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 真少见啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.89,0:16:44.52,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,中井君
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.11,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真野
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这是试炼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能克服这个试炼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.53,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间的羁绊就会更加坚固…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 中井
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友给你送巧克力来了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.84,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么生气了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.31,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到做不到做不到 绝对做不到的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再说那算什么啊 整天和其他男生混在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道我要送他巧克力吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.90,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给我聪明点单独行动啊 真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.49,0:17:41.74,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,他是不是其实压根不怎么想要我的巧克力啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,真野
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.92,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你突然跑开 我就追过来了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.88,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟钝了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力 想要吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.32,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想要
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.12,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要被没收了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是书
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.75,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是把借走的书还给我了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.89,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是书的话就算了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张死了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.15,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了 我很高兴
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你还在生气吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.58,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,迟钝迟钝迟钝迟钝
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.34,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然感觉好累啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.59,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.59,0:19:20.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就去要日比野的巧克力了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.39,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个拉不下脸去要啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.47,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要北条同学的巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.23,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,反正西片你已经收到高木同学的了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.56,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？不…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.56,0:19:35.44,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 我不想听 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.79,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,再…再见了 高木同学
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.24,0:19:47.66,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,结果什么都没有给我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.01,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,还能还给你 太好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.05,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一个
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.80,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也没期待什么的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.35,0:20:11.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也没因为到了情人节而被她捉弄
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.10,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,今天算是大胜利了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.20,0:20:23.78,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.62,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是巧克力？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.74,0:20:29.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,什… 那个…这个是…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.83,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是木村吧 大概是木村的恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.50,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 为什么这么说
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.17,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我知道放这个进去的是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.22,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你觉得是谁？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.27,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得她现在还离你挺近的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.47,0:20:54.85,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉 是高木同学吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.61,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但万一不是的话…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 还会很丢人
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想知道啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.36,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.08,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道今天是什么日子吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.54,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.29,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你说什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.00,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.67,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那给你巧克力哦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.72,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？不要吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.76,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那样的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.93,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,要给我巧克力？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 这个不是高木同学给我的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.10,0:21:35.60,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.19,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.48,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,是义理的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.98,0:21:42.98,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.69,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是这个
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.57,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,「这个」？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.99,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那这一个是？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.71,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,那个巧克力 你知道是谁送的么
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.09,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…谁知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.43,Takagisan - text_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道也行啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:00.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,——JP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,寒いね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,手がかじかんできちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:39.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,寒いの苦手だからなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,カイロ使う?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:52.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:02.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,氷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でかい氷だな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日雨だったもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.74,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“持っていきたい”とか思ってる?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:19.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,思ってないよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.87,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな 小学生じゃあるまいし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.41,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.13,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負しよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.47,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいけど 何するの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.22,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,校門まで  大きい氷を持っていったほうの勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ただし 地面に落としちゃったら  その時点で負け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どう?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:51.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.02,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,お先にどうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:56.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.74,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,大きいの取ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.70,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,学校まで もてばいいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんめ 焦っているな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,悪いが 俺が  この氷を落とすことはない!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜなら 俺は小さいころから氷を見つけると必ず持ち運んでいたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,指が冷たさに強いのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,よって俺の手がかじかんで氷を離すことはない!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.06,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,加えて  高木さんにからかわれた回数の３倍の腕立てを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,厳しく  自分に課している俺にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな氷 大した重さじゃないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,思いつき勝負を仕掛けたことを  後悔するがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんは今日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.57,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺に負ける!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:48.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん　ちょっとね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか 西片が大きい氷持って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うれしがってる小学生みたいだなって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なっ…  別に うれしがってなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.10,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.72,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,惜しかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うかつだった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“落とさせる”  そんな作戦があったか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対にもう気は抜かないぞ  今日こそ勝つんだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.45,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなに力強く握ると  割れちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:32.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,敵の心配か?  余裕だな 高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:38.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも確かに あまり力を入れて割れてしまっては
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ　罰ゲームだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:47.43,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“負けたほうが  勝ったほうの手を温かくする”ね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,よし 分かった  このくらいの力加減か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ?　今何て?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:00.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,負けたほうは  勝ったほうの手を温かくするの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えーっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.41,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,笑い過ぎだろう!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,弱いなぁ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 罰ゲームね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.30,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,何すんの?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 勝ったほうの手 温めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.01,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,それ  ホントに言ってたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.77,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,べ… 別のにしない?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.35,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんとなく…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.27,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.27,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,カイロちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.05,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.13,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.01,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,温かいね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.10,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,外見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やあ 高木さん　おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.32,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.37,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“いい勝負 考えてきた”って  顔してるから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.25,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“当たり”って顔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.12,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,さすが高木さんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…で 何の勝負なの?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,まあいい  今日こそ 俺の勝ちなんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 俺は  昨日と どこか違っています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,さて どこでしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,気分とかじゃなくて?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,外見だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.32,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分からないだろう?　高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.65,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,実は昨日の夜  髪の毛を少しだけ切ったのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,反則スレスレ  ていうか卑怯くさいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,勝ちは勝ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:15.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分かったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:16.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,はぁ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも もうちょっと観察しようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってないな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,カマをかけて 俺の口が滑るのを狙っているな?　高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.05,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうはいくか!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントに どこか違うの?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.60,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,後ろかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,しまった!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ジロジロ見られることを 計算に入れてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.20,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,何してんの!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.20,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,服の下かなと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.70,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,違うよ!　見えるとこだよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,びっくりしすぎだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:06.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,途中でこんなふうにからかわれるのも  計算に入れてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.68,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いつもどおり弱いね 脇腹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.47,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やりたかっただけだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:23.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ち… 近いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,目かなと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.61,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ?　顔赤いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.28,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして違うのって 顔の赤さ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.16,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,においはどうかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:44.87,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,普通だね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 外見だって 外見!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どこかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:55.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか高木さん  本当は答えが分かってるんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.97,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺をからかって  楽しんでいるだけなのでは?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.43,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか見抜かれて?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.65,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなの全く計算に入れてなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり目かな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいなら  ギブアップしてもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.87,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対しない!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:24.87,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.33,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“ギブアップしてもいいよ”ってわざわざ言ってくるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,答えが分かっていないってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:35.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり  ここを しのげば 俺の勝ちだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.47,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どこかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,耳かな?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,違うかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.94,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,タイムア?ップ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ…　そう来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.49,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,答えは?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.53,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,髪の毛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,すぐ変えられる外見なんて  爪か髪の毛ぐらいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,爪じゃなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.30,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,髪かなって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 罰ゲームだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.18,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私もあした  ちょっと外見変えてくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.31,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,次は西片が当ててね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木さんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,恥ずかしくてまじまじ見られないと分かってて…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ほらほら 学校行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,遅れちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,やり返されるのも  計算に入れてなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.96,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,寒くなったねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:51.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.17,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,お… おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,前髪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたの?　その髪　何か変
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,わ… 笑うな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日 ちょっと自分で切ってたら  切り過ぎちゃって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 笑うなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや ムリだよ  面白いんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あんただって  失敗したみたいな前髪のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.96,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ほ… 本当に?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そうよ　似たようなもんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗したみたいな前髪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.18,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,結構 気に入ってたのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん ミナ　ちょっと言い過ぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,似合ってるよ その前髪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.61,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私のほうこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.82,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,友達なら 励まさなきゃ  いけないとこだったのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.33,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,笑っちゃって…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんね ユカリちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.01,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.97,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.35,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう　今日も寒いね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,お… おはよう 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.60,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:37.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタインデー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,落ち着け 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心 平常心だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,な… なに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.66,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日って 体育あったっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　なかったと思うけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだよね　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もしかして この中に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かからのチョコが入っていたり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.02,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…しないよな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.86,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,な… なに!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.57,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今 ゲタ箱開けてちょっとがっかりしてたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.03,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうかしたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:33.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ いや…べ… 別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,何でもないから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,紫式部の「源氏物語」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:46.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,清少納言の「枕草子」も  研究の対象となっていました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,先生も中学のときには…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.14,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,い…いや…バレンタインだからって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.02,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,別に期待してるわけじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.94,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ  むしろこんな日だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.81,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺を からかってくるはずだ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.07,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,気をつけよう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.24,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,は… はい!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.16,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,消しゴム 貸してくれない?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.66,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.37,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,これは もしや
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,消しゴムを返すついでに  さりげな?くチョコなんかを…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら どうしよう!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.42,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:22.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.72,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そう言ったんだよ  それって笑えるだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:35.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.10,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.06,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうやって渡そう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:43.73,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,みんな?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日 バレンタインだから  チョコいっぱい作ってきたよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.70,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,欲しい人は どうぞ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.91,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ウソ!?　愛の手作りチョコ?  女子力 たかっ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.96,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ 私 欲しい!私も!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あんなに愛をばらまいて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おいしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.13,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ちゃんと配れよ 日々野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もらいに行けるわけねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私も  ミナちゃんみたいな性格だったらな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.40,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“チョコは見つけしだい没収”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.65,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そう言ったよな?　日々野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:34.87,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,没収
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.04,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか　先生にも気をつけないと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,渡せるのかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.63,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ひどいよ 没収なんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.22,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私 まだもらってないのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きを見るのね  むやみに愛をばらまくと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:02.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　もう渡したのかなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.19,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,渡したっていえば 渡したのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ど… どうやって?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,朝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:13.70,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,  いいの?　それで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:14.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:21.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,高木ちゃんも恥ずかしいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 私は手渡ししたい  なんとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.46,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そのほうが  気持ちが伝わる気がするし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:34.26,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,でも  これじゃ まるで試練だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,海沿いにあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:38.64,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,マジか!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:39.51,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,見てこいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,絶対すごいって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,へえ…　珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:44.52,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,中井君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:47.11,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おう 真野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　試練よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,これを乗り越えれば
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.53,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちの絆は より強く…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.12,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いいな 中井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,彼女からチョコだぞ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おい!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,羨ましい!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.84,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで怒ってんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.31,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.60,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ムリムリムリ!　絶対ムリ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…ていうか なんなの!?  いっつも男子と一緒にいてさ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコ渡すって分かるでしょう!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.90,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,気を利かせて  1人行動くらいしてよね! もう?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:41.74,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,私のチョコ 別に欲しくないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バカ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,真野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.92,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,急に逃げるから追っかけてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.88,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ　なに怒ってんだよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,鈍感!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコ  要る?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.32,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　欲しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:18.61,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.12,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,没収…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,本です!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:31.75,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,貸してた本  返してもらってただけで…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.89,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,本なら まあいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,緊張した
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.15,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとな　うれしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なあ　まだ怒ってんのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.58,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,鈍感 鈍感 鈍感 鈍感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.34,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか どっと疲れたな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:15.59,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:20.05,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,日々野のチョコ  もらっとくんだったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.39,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あれはもらえねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.47,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は  北条さんにもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:30.23,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,どうせ西片は高木さんにもらったんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.56,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ?　いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:35.44,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,アーッ!　アア…　聞きたくない!やめてくれ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.79,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ… じゃあね 高木さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:47.66,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,結局 何もなかったー!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.01,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,良かったね 返してもらえて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:00.05,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,2人とも食べて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.80,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや…  別に期待なんてしてなかったさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:11.27,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタインのことで  からかわれなかったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.10,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は大勝利さ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:23.78,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.62,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ チョコ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:29.08,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,なっ…　え?っと これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.83,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,き…木村かな  多分 木村のいたずらじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.50,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.67,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ?な… なんで?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.17,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,だって  私 それ入れたの誰か知ってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.22,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ  誰だと思う?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.27,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今 結構近くにいると思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:54.85,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,こ… この感じは 高木さんだな?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:58.61,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　でも 万が一にも違ったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,それに なんか恥ずかしいし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,べ…別に知りたくないし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.36,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ふ?ん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:10.08,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,今日って 何の日か知ってる?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.54,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタイン…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.29,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,う?ん?　なぁに?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,バレンタイン!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.00,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,正解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.67,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ チョコあげるね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.72,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,うん?　要らない?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.76,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,いや　別に そういうんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.93,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,チョコをくれる?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.60,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,…てことは  これは高木さんからじゃないのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:35.60,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.19,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.48,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,義理だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:42.98,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってるよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.69,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,こっちはね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:46.57,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,“こっちは”?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.99,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ こっちは?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.71,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,そのチョコ 誰からか分かる?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.09,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,さ… さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.43,Takagisan - text_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,分からなくていいから
